									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://michaelbastos.com/tag/cheaper/" rel="tag">cheaper</a>, <a href="http://michaelbastos.com/tag/commodity/" rel="tag">commodity</a>, <a href="http://michaelbastos.com/tag/design/" rel="tag">design</a>, <a href="http://michaelbastos.com/tag/web-design/" rel="tag">Web Design</a>			</span>
						
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
						<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://michaelbastos.com/2011/05/06/why-web-design-has-now-become-a-commodity-and-will-get-cheaper-and-cheaper/#comments" title="Comment on Web Design as a Commodity"><b>4</b> Replies</a></span>
			
