				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://michaelbastos.com/tag/chaos-monkey/" rel="tag">chaos monkey</a>, <a href="http://michaelbastos.com/tag/netflix/" rel="tag">Netflix</a>, <a href="http://michaelbastos.com/tag/networks/" rel="tag">networks</a>, <a href="http://michaelbastos.com/tag/traffic/" rel="tag">traffic</a>			</span>
						
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
						<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://michaelbastos.com/2011/04/26/how-netflix-uses-chaos-monkey-to-take-down-its-own-networks-so-that-they-never-go-down/#respond" title="Comment on Chaos Monkey saves Netflix"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></a></span>
			
